=Example=

==Ghent==

"Local School Gent, Belguim - Hosted by Timelab

Yearly evening school in 10 lessons of 3 hours

From Oct 3 until Dec 19, weekly on Thursday from 7pm to 10pm

12 participants work in 4 teams on a real and local case in the neighbourhood. You learn how to apply 8 patterns to the case in a practical manner so you can easily copy your learnings to your own project. The other participants and coaches of the School of Commons become your network of peers in learning and provide feedback .

12 students of partner Howest help your team to immlement the commoning process.

Language: Dutch

From October 3rd to December 19th, every thursdayevening from 19-22 p.m. except november first.

Venue: De Schuur, kogelstraat 34, 9000 Gent."


